metadata.name: choose
metadata.description:
Hearing this, Stubbs replied, "You've been in this situation before."



"Is there a solution?" Zhang Ping asked eagerly.



Stu shi Bai replied, "Yes, the solution is not difficult, just need to meditate, ask, determine their own path."



"Meditate, ask questions, determine your path?" Zhang Ping frowned, puzzled.



Stu shi Bai explained: "In fact, this situation only occurs in awakened people with multiple abilities. Awakened people with a single ability often decide the path they want to take very early, and the more abilities they have, the more options they have, which will cause the awakened person to have 'level stagnation' when they level up.
